Class App

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • FinalProject.App

  • public class App
extends javafx.application.Application
    JavaFX App

    The heart of the program. This class handles the window, containers within the window, and placing the search results into those containers.

      • processSearch

        public void processSearch(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        Processes a search, linked to the search box. This method first removes any tabs currently open, then creates a new tab with the search results for the search term. The search term is taken from the search box.
